titles.title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on Trifluoromethylaniline.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S4857)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 4/22/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1996, the suspension of duty on trifluoromethylaniline.
